# --- PRODUCCIÓN ---

### 2.1 Listar maniquíes (Protegido)
GET {{baseUrl}}/maniquies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.2 Ensamblar unidad (Stored Procedure - Solo Gerente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/maniquies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "modelo_id": 1,
  "numero_serie": "SENIOR-MOD-01",
  "numero_lote": "LOTE-MAY24"
}

# --- INVENTARIO ---

### 3.1 Registrar pieza (Trigger Serial)
POST {{baseUrl}}/piezas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tipo_parte_id": 1, 
  "modelo_id": 1,
  "origen_id": 1,
  "tono_acabado_id": 1,
  "costo": 250.00
}

### 3.2 Trazabilidad de pieza
GET {{baseUrl}}/piezas/PZ-CAB-INT-0001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.3 Ensamblar (Anti-Frankenstein FAIL - Trigger 409)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/piezas/PZ-CAB-INT-0001/ensamblar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Prefer: code=409

{
  "maniqui_id": 99
}

# --- CATÁLOGOS ---

### 4.1 Listar Modelos Técnicos
GET {{baseUrl}}/modelos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.2 Listar Tipos de Parte
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalogos/tipos-parte
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# --- ANALÍTICA ---

### 5.1 Cálculo de Descuento (UDF SQL)
GET {{baseUrl}}/modelos/1/descuento?porcentaje=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.2 Dashboard de Producción (Vista SQL)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reportes/produccion
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
